    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为上帝的代理人，玩家获得了上帝的力量，并踏上了对抗不守规矩的生物的旅程，以恢复它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161990/extras/1665a3652171dc8760ae72c49d1700d0.avif?t=1734543086\" width=200 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款类魂游戏，你可以通过招架、翻滚和守护来击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161990/extras/5792030cf7f4480f6fbccc9e090e8a86.poster.avif?t=1734543086\" width=200 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161990/extras/5792030cf7f4480f6fbccc9e090e8a86.webm?t=1734543086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161990/extras/5792030cf7f4480f6fbccc9e090e8a86.mp4?t=1734543086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以玩 Harmagedon 游戏教程部分，其中包含 1 种怪物和 1 种 Boss。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[未来发布的功能和内容]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[列表]</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 额外的普通怪物和头目怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 各种类型的盔甲</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 升级系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 剑和盾以外的武器（魔法、巨剑、弓等）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/列表]</p>",
